By BO Staff Writer The following statement was previously published on the Black First Land First website: Black First Land First (BLF) sends its heartfelt condolences to the Deputy President Comrade Zanele Lwana and her extended family on the passing of her father. Our movement wishes the family strength during this period. May our Gods comfort them all. BLF shall keep our members and the public informed of the funeral arrangements as soon as they have been finalized. Lala ngoxolo Dlomo! Issued by Black First Land First, National Coordinating Committee of (BLF NCC) 30 October 2019 Contact Details Black First Land First Mail: blackfirstlandfirst@gmail.com Andile Mngxitama
(BLF President)
